<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the picket line</b></font><BR>
<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">July 5, 2002 | Page 11</font></p>

<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"> OTHER STORIES BELOW<BR>
<A HREF="#Wheels Transportation">Wheels Transportation</A><BR>
<A HREF="#Village Voice">Village Voice</A><BR>
